title: Railworks TS2015 AP Class 55 Sound Pack (Pro)
description:
As requested, updated sound pack. Sound fading fix 04.10.2014

During the installation process, these sounds will be applied to both the BR blue & green liveried class 55s contained within the RS.com European Community Asset Pack and also the BR DP1 Deltic Loco Add-on.



Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.
